clonevar changeterm = term
recode changeterm (1946=0)(1947=0)(1948=0)(1949=1)(1950=0)(1951=0)(1952=0)(1953=1)(1954=1)(1955=0)(1956=1)(1957=0)(1958=1)(1959=0)(1960=0)(1961=1)(1962=1)(1963=0)(1964=0)(1965=1)(1966=0)(1967=1)(1968=0)(1969=1)(1970=0)(1971=1)(1972=0)(1973=0)(1974=0)(1975=1)(1976=0)(1977=0)(1978=0)(1979=0)(1980=0)(1981=1)(1982=0)(1983=0)(1984=0)(1985=0)(1986=1)(1987=1)(1988=0)(1989=0)(1990=1)(1991=1)(1992=0)(1993=1)(1994=1)(1995=0)(1996=0)(1997=0)(1998=0)(1999=0)(2000=0)(2001=0)(2002=0)(2003=0)(2004=0)(2005=1)(2006=0)(2007=0)(2008=0)(2009=1)(2010=0)(2011=0)(2012=0)(2013=0)(2014=0)(2015=0)(2016=1)(2017=0)(2018=1)(2019=0)(2020=1)(2021=0)(2022=1), gen(change_in_comp)
label define varchangeincomp 1 "Change in Composition" 0 "No Change in Composition "
label values change_in_comp varchangeincomp
drop if term < 1946		


